snippet.title: Siren Head: The Arrival [OFFICIAL MOD RELEASE TRAILER]
snippet.description:
#sirenhead #minecrafthorror #minecraft #horrorgaming #newmods #mods #modded #moddedminecraft #mc 

Music used in the video by Infraction: 
Insidious by Infraction
https://inaudio.org/track/insidious-horror/
Music promoted by Inaudio: http://bit.ly/3qxoX6U

The official RELEASE trailer for the minecraft horror mod Siren Head. The mod is inspired by Trevor Henderson's Siren Head creature (obviously), and is developed by the creators of the Dangers In The Darkness mod, sound design is done by @Rupter-hc5dd and the project is directed / coordinated by me.
MOD DOWNLOAD: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/siren-head-the-arrival

Buckle up, because things are about to get LOUD.

JOIN OUR DISCORD: https://discord.gg/QDGsjmpSHT
